<p><img src="/media/13072364/skier-off-piste.jpg" alt="New Ski Holidays Winter 2019 and 2020" data-udi="umb://media/ea43cce84bc84d6eaa22502e2316e3b7" /></p>
<p><span class="geolocation-title"><a name="top"></a>Book now to take advantage of our top offers, there is no better time to book your 2019/20 ski holiday. </span></p>
<div class="data-grid" style="float: center;">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="tablet-button" style="height: 20px; width: 300px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td width="auto" height="20" align="center" valign="middle" style="background-color: #f26419; border-radius: 4px; background-clip: padding-box; font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; padding-left: 18px; padding-right: 18px;"><a style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none;" data-udi="umb://document/c511f5b016b94e78afe01f1584da0f77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c511f5b016b94e78afe01f1584da0f77}" title="Ski 2019/20 Deals">Search our ski deals</a></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Our Fab 5 Offers for 2019/20<br /><br /></h2>
<img src="/media/13074533/website-image.jpg" alt="Group of skiers" data-udi="umb://media/14394f55c62041d1bf07c3193afb4365" /><br />
<h2><strong><br />Offer 1   6 nights catering in our Chalets &amp; Chalet Hotels</strong></h2>
<p>We know that for most of our guests your ski holiday is not only about making the most of the slopes, but also an escape from the everyday routine. We’ve been listening to your feedback and are pleased to announce that 6 nights’ catering is back in all our chalets as well as in our chalet hotels.</p>
<h2><strong>Offer 2   Ski in a group <a data-udi="umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb}" title="Group Ski Holidays">1-in-6 go FREE</a></strong></h2>
<p>If you are looking to book a group of more than 7 people, up to 1 person in 5* goes FREE. Terms and Conditions apply.</p>
<h2><strong>Offer 3   2 - for - 1 Ski/Board &amp; Boot Hire  </strong></h2>
<p>Pre-book your lift pass when you confirm your reservation and receive 2-for-1 red or blue skis/board and boot hire. Offer applies to all ski holidays in <a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austria</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy">Italy</a>.</p>
<h2>Offer 4<strong>   Inghams Plus Offers</strong></h2>
<p>Get even more from your ski holiday with our partner hotel offers. These offers can include FREE drinks with dinner; FREE room upgrades; FREE packed lunches; FREE activities and so much more. See individual hotel pages for specific offers.</p>
<h2><strong>Offer 5   Early Booking Offers</strong></h2>
<p>Our partner-hotels reward early bookers with discounts, which can be considerable. Applicable discounts are <strong>included</strong> in our prices and are subject to availability.</p>
<p align="right"><span class="geolocation-title"><a href="/ski-holidays/special-offers/ski-holidays-for-winter-20192020#top" title="top">^ Return to top</a></span></p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Ski in a Group: up to 1 in 6* go FREE<br /><br /></h2>
<p><strong><img src="/media/13072359/apres.jpg" alt="Group Ski Holidays" data-udi="umb://media/432ea8fc7fca4527801adee83cc85e81" /></strong></p>
<p>Inghams Ski is the best specialist to trust with your ski group holiday. We have the experience to help you find the right accommodation to ensure everyone in your group is satisfied.</p>
<p>Book your group ski holiday early and you have the added bonus of being able to combine our above groups offer and 2-for-1 ski/board hire offer.</p>
<p>Other benefits for groups include:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Exclusive private transfers for groups of 25 or more</strong></li>
<li><strong>Free lift pass for the party leader of groups of 15 or more</strong></li>
<li><strong>Flexible flying - fly from different airports in the UK to join your group<br /><br /></strong></li>
</ul>
<p><a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb}" target="_blank" title="Group Ski Holidays"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
<p align="right"><span class="geolocation-title"><a href="/ski-holidays/special-offers/ski-holidays-for-winter-20192020#top" title="top">^ Return to top</a></span></p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2>Family Ski Holidays</h2>
<p><strong><img src="/media/13072363/selfie-stick.jpg" alt="Family Ski Holidays" data-udi="umb://media/b9b0855d1e4742e8a06440bac4dc4a43" /></strong></p>
<p>Take advantage of some fantastic value offers on children's lift passes, ski hire and tuition to make your family ski holiday great value for money. See individual resort pages for details.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/edec03d1756a4a76b5b9fa0c20b36400" href="/{localLink:umb://document/edec03d1756a4a76b5b9fa0c20b36400}" title="Family Ski Holidays"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
<p align="right"><span class="geolocation-title"><a href="/ski-holidays/special-offers/ski-holidays-for-winter-20192020#top" title="top">^ Return to top</a></span></p>
</div>
